high_descs: walk forwards to the end of the room with the long white table, then turn right and walk forwards to the black small table
grab the butter knife off of the table
cut the apple with the butter knife
back up a bit and face the kitchen table to your left
place the butter knife on the kitchen table to the right of the soap dispenser
turn right and walk forwards a bit to the black table again
pick up an apple slice off of the black table
turn around and walk over to the microwave in the left corner of the room
place the apple inside of the microwave, cook it, then take it back out
turn around and walk over to the black table again on the opposite side corner of the room
place the apple on top of the black table there
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved apple slice on top of the black table

high_descs: Go forward towards the white table and then turn right to face the small brown table.
Pick up the knife off of the table.
Slice the apply on the brown table.
Turn around and to your right face the white table.
cut the loaf of bread on the table.
Turn back to face the brown table on your right.
Pick up a slice of the apple off of the table.
Turn around and head left, then turn right to face the microwave on the white table in the corner.
Put the apple in the microwave and turn on the microwave and then open the microwave and take the apple out.
Turn to your left and then left again and head back to the brown table on your right.
Put the apple slice on the brown table.
anns.task_desc: Heating up a piece of apple.

high_descs: Walk to the small black table to the right of the black trash bag in the corner.
Pick up the knife from the black table.
Cut up the yellow apple near the front of the small black table.
Turn left to face the table with bread on it.
Place the knife on top of the bread on the table.
Turn right to face the small black table.
Pick up a piece of the cut up yellow apple.
Turn right and walk to the microwave next to the trash can in the opposite corner of the room.
Microwave the piece of apple and then pick the piece of apple up and close the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the small black table in the opposite corner of the room.
Place the piece of apple next to the salt shakers on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved piece of a yellow apple on the black table next to the trash bag.

high_descs: Go to the table that is to the left of the the kitchen sink counter
Pick up the knife on the table that is to the right of the apple.
With the knife slice the apple in half.
With the knife go to the white table that the toaster is on
Put the knife on top of the loaf of bread that is on the right side of the table.
Turn and go to the table that is to the left of the kitchen sink counter
Grab a slice of the apple.
Turn and with the slice of apple go to the microwave.
Open the microwave.  Put the apple slice to the left of the item that is in the microwave.  Close the door.  Start the microwave for thirty seconds.  Open the door and grab the slice of the apple.
Turn and with the apple slice go to the table that is to the left of the kitchen sink counter.
Put the apple slice on the table to the left of the two salt shakers that are in front of the bottle of lotion.
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple slice to warm it up.
